2
00:00:04,559 --> 00:00:07,679
to help the employer recognize
your resume from someone elses.

3
00:00:07,679 --> 00:00:10,922
It should contain the appropriate
contact information and

4
00:00:10,922 --> 00:00:12,929
link to your other online profiles,

5
00:00:12,929 --> 00:00:15,859
in case the employer wants
to find out more about you.

6
00:00:15,859 --> 00:00:19,298
Then the rest of your resume is about
providing evidence that you are job

7
00:00:19,298 --> 00:00:19,710
ready.

8
00:00:21,469 --> 00:00:25,619
You want to include the education and
work experiences you have.

9
00:00:25,620 --> 00:00:29,336
If you feel like one of these
sections will not be very strong,

10
00:00:29,335 --> 00:00:30,557
emphasize others.

11
